prompt_text: Describe the people of any new place you have visited recently.
content_text: I had recently visited Buckley's office in order. It was a very. Large office. And the people were there. Very good. It was a highly organized place. The lifts were working at very fast state. And there were huge workspaces for the employees to work. I can see the gigantic screens. Those systems were working very efficiently. We had a coffee machine there and free lunches and breakfasts were provided.
